textfsm_template:
Value PORT (\S+)
Value TYPE (\S+)
Value SPEED (\d+G?)
Value DESCRIPTION (\S.*?)

Start
  ^Interface\s+Description\s*$$ -> Begin

Begin
  ^-+
  ^Port\s+Type\s+Speed\s+Description\s*$$
  ^Interface\s+Description\s*$$
  ^${PORT}\s+${TYPE}\s+${SPEED}(?:\s+${DESCRIPTION})?\s*$$ -> Record
  ^${PORT}\s+(?:\s+${DESCRIPTION})?\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
